5
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:50,220
（命运）

6
00:01:00,380 --> 00:01:09,260
（人族帝国）

7
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:42,560
她回来了
She's back!

8
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,771
她回家了
She's home!

9
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,920
菲莉帕回家了
Philippa came home!

10
00:02:26,614 --> 00:02:30,082
两年过去了
Two years,

11
00:02:30,083 --> 00:02:34,154
一切都还和我记忆中一样
and everything looks exactly as I remember.

12
00:02:35,623 --> 00:02:39,159
我本以为自己永远没法回家了
I never thought I would see this place again.

13
00:02:42,180 --> 00:02:45,666
这次我们有18人
There were 18 of us this time.

14
00:02:45,666 --> 00:02:49,740
都是从帝国的各个角落
Culled from every corner of the Empire

15
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:52,139
被抓到地球参加比赛
and brought to Terra for the contest.

16
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:55,608
我们被告知 接下来的几年里
We were told that only one of us would survive

17
00:02:55,609 --> 00:02:57,878
我们当中只有一个人能活下来
the years to come.

18
00:02:58,740 --> 00:03:01,114
只有一个孩子
One child

19
00:03:02,850 --> 00:03:06,887
能代表最纯粹的地球血统
the purest expression of the Terran identity.

20
00:03:07,755 --> 00:03:11,124
他们让我们互相残杀
They pitted us against each other.

21
00:03:11,124 --> 00:03:15,229
过了一个又一个月 人数逐渐减少
And month by month, our numbers dwindled.

22
00:03:17,064 --> 00:03:20,368
那 你赢了吗
Did... did you win?

23
00:03:21,369 --> 00:03:23,040
比赛结束了吗
Is it over?

24
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:25,939
还有两个人活着
Two of us still live.

25
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:34,582
桑和我
San and me.

26
00:03:36,917 --> 00:03:38,886
我和桑
Me and San.

27
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:44,758
我们
We are two

28
00:03:44,758 --> 00:03:46,200
双生一体
but one.

29
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,716
直至永恒
Forever.

30
00:03:51,221 --> 00:03:53,301
竞赛当中禁止出现「朋友」这个词
The word "friend" was forbidden during the contest,

31
00:03:53,301 --> 00:03:56,604
但我们在别人听不到的时候向对方耳语说出这个词
but we whispered it to each other when no one could hear.

32
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,300
桑和我将我们的技能结合起来
San and I combined our skills

33
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:03,320
一起对付监察者和其他参赛者
against the proctor and the other contestants.

34
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:06,113
但你们当中只有一个人能成为皇帝
But only one of you could be emperor.

35
00:04:08,516 --> 00:04:10,518
还剩下最后一个任务
One task remains.

36
00:04:13,487 --> 00:04:14,922
最先完成任务的人就可以统治帝国
The first to complete it rules the Empire,

37
00:04:14,922 --> 00:04:16,600
而另一个人
and the other spends the rest of their life

38
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:19,140
将终生侍奉新皇
in servitude to the new emperor.

39
00:04:19,140 --> 00:04:21,194
你要做什么
What do you have to do?

40
00:04:37,845 --> 00:04:39,078
我很抱歉
I'm sorry.

41
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:41,048
你做了什么
What did you do?!

42
00:04:42,115 --> 00:04:46,052
一切旧日牵绊 皆不可再续
No ties to the old life are permitted.

43
00:04:47,421 --> 00:04:50,791
人族的帝皇唯忠于职责
An emperor can only be loyal to duty.

44
00:04:50,791 --> 00:04:54,894
如此帝国方能强盛
Thus does the Empire remain strong.

45
00:04:54,895 --> 00:04:57,365
如此帝国方能扩张
Thus does it grow.

46
00:05:01,134 --> 00:05:02,380
妈妈
Mom.

47
00:05:02,380 --> 00:05:03,626
菲莉帕
Philippa.

48
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:35,340
你完成了你的对手无法下手的任务
You succeeded where your competitor could not.

49
00:06:37,197 --> 00:06:39,833
把他带过来
Bring him here.

50
00:06:41,835 --> 00:06:45,872
桑缺乏勇气 没能通过最后的试炼
San did not have the strength to pass the final test.

51
00:06:45,873 --> 00:06:51,479
现在 他的村庄仍在烈火中燃烧 昭示着他的懦弱
Even now, his village burns as a testament to his cowardice.

52
00:06:54,515 --> 00:06:56,584
我爱你
I love you.

53
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,654
你赢得了比赛
You have won the contest.

54
00:07:00,654 --> 00:07:04,056
宣布你的胜利吧
Claim your victory.

55
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:22,242
桑  走上前
San, step forward.

56
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:26,814
现在你的生命只为侍奉于她的足下
You live now only to serve at her heel.

57
00:07:38,992 --> 00:07:42,362
跪下 向主宰你生命的皇帝臣服
Kneel before the one who owns your life.

58
00:07:55,108 --> 00:07:57,578
我们双生
We are two...

59
00:07:58,779 --> 00:08:00,147
一体
But one.

60
00:08:01,715 --> 00:08:03,584
不再是了
Not anymore.

61
00:08:30,477 --> 00:08:33,981
菲莉帕·乔久万岁
All hail Philippa Georgiou!

62
00:08:34,081 --> 00:08:35,783
皇帝万岁
All hail the emperor!

63
00:08:37,160 --> 00:08:41,380
万岁 万岁
Hail! Hail!

64
00:08:56,540 --> 00:08:57,671
我是总控
This is Control

65
00:08:57,671 --> 00:09:00,540
有一条发给阿尔法小队队长的最高优先级讯息
with a priority message for Alpha Team Leader.

66
00:09:01,775 --> 00:09:04,945
你们的新目标是菲莉帕·乔久皇帝
Your subject is Emperor Philippa Georgiou,

67
00:09:05,045 --> 00:09:07,715
地球帝国前任统治者
former ruler of the Terran Empire.

68
00:09:07,715 --> 00:09:09,381
地球帝国存在于一个平行宇宙
It's in a parallel universe

69
00:09:09,382 --> 00:09:11,780
在已知历史记录中
with the most criminal population

70
00:09:11,780 --> 00:09:13,153
该帝国的臣民最为残暴
in recorded history.

71
00:09:14,154 --> 00:09:17,658
即使在那个宇宙 乔久仍能以暴政完全掌控帝国的每个角落
Even there, Georgiou had the market cornered on atrocities.

72
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:23,780
2257年 她被带到我们的宇宙
In 2257, she was brought to our universe

73
00:09:23,780 --> 00:09:25,960
并加入31区
and joined Section 31,

74
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:28,840
但几年后 我们失去了联络
but after a few years, we lost contact.

75
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,740
（联络丢失）

76
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:33,420
近日 我们联邦领土边境外的区域
Recently, Georgiou was spotted using an alias

77
00:09:33,420 --> 00:09:36,442
发现菲莉帕·乔久以化名出现
in the border territory outside Federation space,

78
00:09:36,443 --> 00:09:40,900
该地正是我们追踪黑市新威胁的关键区域
where we're tracking a new threat on the black market.

79
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:42,883
接下来的任务，就交给你们了
This is where your team comes in.

80
00:09:42,883 --> 00:09:47,140
联邦签订的条约禁止我们跨越边界
Federation treaty forbids us from crossing over that border,

81
00:09:47,140 --> 00:09:50,660
也就意味着星际舰队不能暗中行事
which means Starfleet cannot get its hands dirty.

82
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:53,827
你和你31区的队伍将前往与乔久联络
You and your 31 team will go in, make contact with Georgiou

83
00:09:53,827 --> 00:09:57,300
发现并控制那个威胁
to help identify and neutralize the threat.

84
00:09:58,420 --> 00:10:01,068
但需注意
But make no mistake

85
00:10:01,068 --> 00:10:04,972
恶犬咬人 多加小心
this dog bites, so watch your backs.

86
00:10:05,806 --> 00:10:08,575
你们只有24小时的时间完成任务
You have 24 hours to complete the mission.

87
00:10:08,575 --> 00:10:09,560
动身吧
Get to work.

88
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:11,560
（通讯结束）

89
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:24,140
（星际迷航：31区）
（星际迷航中国字幕组译制）

90
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,460
（星历 1292.4）

91
00:10:42,460 --> 00:10:48,100
（星际联邦领空之外）

92
00:11:48,608 --> 00:11:49,980
杜·弗朗克女士
Madame du Franc?

93
00:11:50,911 --> 00:11:53,480
蜜月套房里出了个小事故
Small incident in the honeymoon suite.

94
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,740
似乎是一位新娘
I'm afraid the bride molted

95
00:11:55,740 --> 00:11:57,751
在快到高潮的时候蜕皮了
just as things were coming to a climax.

96
00:11:57,751 --> 00:12:00,640
维吉尔 说重点
Virgil,get to the point.

97
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:04,300
我派出了一支生化小队 并致以你的吊唁
I sent a biohazard team and your condolences.

98
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:08,829
另外 有一位顾客想和你说句话
Also, there's a customer hoping for a word with you.

99
00:12:09,629 --> 00:12:13,500
他看起来很清醒 但已经喝了不少
He seems entirely sober but quite intoxicating.

100
00:12:19,672 --> 00:12:22,575
维罗妮克·杜·弗朗克女士同意见你
Madame Veronique du Franc will see you.

101
00:12:30,984 --> 00:12:34,280
阿洛克·萨哈  这位是维罗妮克·杜·弗朗克女士
Alok Sahar, Madame Veronique du Franc.

102
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:37,040
杜·弗朗克女士一般只接受预约洽谈
Madame du Franc normally does business by appointment.

103
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:38,940
那我想预约一下
I'd like to make an appointment.

104
00:12:38,940 --> 00:12:41,600
噢 这位绅士想预约一下
Oh, the gentleman would like to make an appointment.

105
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:42,540
就约现在
Now.

106
00:12:42,540 --> 00:12:43,920
他说就约现在 女士
Now, madame.

107
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:44,940
（法语）
Impossible.

108
00:12:44,940 --> 00:12:46,284
她说不可能
Impossible.

109
00:12:58,278 --> 00:13:00,547
先退下吧 维吉尔
Au revoir, Virgil.

110
00:13:18,140 --> 00:13:19,040
这玩意儿是非法的
That is illegal.

111
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,701
但能赚大钱
And that makes money.

112
00:13:21,701 --> 00:13:23,871
我这里是声誉良好的生意场所
This is a reputable establishment.

113
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,800
据我所知可不是这样
Not what I heard.

114
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:27,806
我们为什么不去你的办公室讨论呢
Why don't we discuss it in your office?

115
00:13:27,807 --> 00:13:32,340
我为什么要带你去我的办公室呢 阿洛克·萨哈
Why would I take you to my office, Alok Sahar?

116
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:35,916
因为这玩意儿得自己试试
Because it's a hands-on experience.

117
00:13:46,994 --> 00:13:48,694
我所到之处
♪ Everywhere I go ♪

118
00:13:48,695 --> 00:13:50,362
人尽皆知
♪ Everybody knows... ♪

119
00:13:52,665 --> 00:13:54,868
悦耳蓟
Dulcet thistle.

120
00:13:54,868 --> 00:13:57,860
悦耳蓟已经灭绝了
Dulcet thistle's extinct.

121
00:13:57,860 --> 00:13:59,640
我有很多存货
I've got a dozen keys of this stuff.

122
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:02,075
你要来点吗
Have you partaken?

123
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:07,414
这将是我为数不多的几次初体验
This would be one of my few first times.

124
00:14:07,414 --> 00:14:09,381
来一杯潘趣酒
Packs a punch.

125
00:14:09,382 --> 00:14:12,285
快乐的一杯
A happy punch.

126
00:14:21,227 --> 00:14:22,762
干杯
Bottoms up.

127
00:14:22,762 --> 00:14:23,940
敬赚钱
To money.

128
00:14:23,940 --> 00:14:24,720
敬你
To you.

129
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:42,109
好了 别说废话了
Now, let's cut the shit.

130
00:14:42,900 --> 00:14:46,040
31区来我的空间站干什么
What is Section 31 doing in my space station?

131
00:14:46,040 --> 00:14:49,400
你觉得我会认不出来一个特工吗
Hmm? You think I don't know an agent when I see one?

132
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:50,991
你带领着一个六人小队
You're heading up a team of six operatives,

133
00:14:51,124 --> 00:14:53,460
分散在这个酒吧里
and they're all over the bar.

134
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,497
有一个查莫人
There's the Chameloid,

135
00:14:57,497 --> 00:15:00,200
一个绿血变形人
a green-blooded shape-shifter,

136
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:04,171
假装在与一个德尔塔人*调情寻欢
trying to muster sexy time with a Deltan,

137
00:15:04,271 --> 00:15:05,904
多么甜蜜的人形陷阱
a walking honey trap

138
00:15:05,905 --> 00:15:09,142
31区用来转移注意力的惯用伎俩
31's obviously using as a distraction.

139
00:15:09,242 --> 00:15:13,112
可实际上查莫人是银河系里唯一
Except Chameloids are the only species in the galaxy

140
00:15:13,113 --> 00:15:16,749
对德尔塔人的魅惑能力保持免疫的种族
immune to Deltan sexy time charm.

141
00:15:16,849 --> 00:15:20,320
然后是那个穿着一身高端器械的家伙
Then there's the guy with all the high-end mech,

142
00:15:20,453 --> 00:15:24,456
傻站在后面 显得好像他有脑子似的
standing in the back, looking like he has thoughts.

143
00:15:24,457 --> 00:15:27,459
机械生命 有的可不只是蛮力
Mech life, it ain't just about the brute force.

144
00:15:29,529 --> 00:15:33,266
实际上更头脑简单 四肢发达
I'm gonna say heavy on artillery, low on IQ.

145
00:15:33,266 --> 00:15:35,202
我很抱歉
I'm so sorry.

146
00:15:35,202 --> 00:15:37,020
还有那位瓦肯人
And we can't forget the Vulcan,

147
00:15:37,020 --> 00:15:40,340
被舞台表演逗得哈哈大笑
laughing way too hard at the stage banter.

148
00:15:43,900 --> 00:15:47,347
鉴于瓦肯人从来不笑 他要么也是个白痴
And since Vulcans never laugh, he's either an idiot, too,

149
00:15:47,347 --> 00:15:50,817
要么就是在庞发期间脑子变得不正常了
or lost his mind during pon farr and went insane.

150
00:15:52,885 --> 00:15:54,754
拜托 那明明很好笑啊
Oh, come on. That was funny.

151
00:15:54,754 --> 00:15:57,840
还有你安排给他那个特别正经的人类搭档
And the very serious human you stuck him with...

152
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:59,292
你控制一下自己
Reel it in anytime.

153
00:15:59,292 --> 00:16:02,000
她看着就是一副苦大仇深的样子
...she's got a stick so far up her backside,

154
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,440
一开口就能听出来
it's coming out her mouth.

155
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:05,065
冷静一点
Just reel it in.

156
00:16:09,300 --> 00:16:10,920
那位是
That would be

157
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:12,500
加勒特上尉*
Lieutenant Garrett.

158
00:16:13,273 --> 00:16:14,580
星际舰队的
Starfleet.

159
00:16:15,540 --> 00:16:19,746
无趣到死
Where fun goes to die.

160
00:16:19,746 --> 00:16:23,016
你找我花了不少时间啊
It took you long enough to find me.

161
00:16:23,016 --> 00:16:26,380
只要你留在巴拉姆空间站
We knew that having you here on the Baraam

162
00:16:26,380 --> 00:16:28,321
对我们来说 总有一天会派上用场
would be valuable to us one day.

163
00:16:28,860 --> 00:16:32,420
好吧 我不得不说我一点儿也不感动
Well, I'm not feeling motivated to be valuable

164
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:34,894
我只为自己所用
to anyone but myself.

165
00:16:38,097 --> 00:16:42,202
今夜请说愿意
♪ Say yes tonight ♪

166
00:16:42,202 --> 00:16:45,660
一切都可应允
♪ Say yes to everything... ♪

167
00:16:45,660 --> 00:16:49,008
所以 我们就这么开始谈判？
So, is this where we start negotiating?

168
00:16:49,008 --> 00:16:51,210
那要看情况了
Hmm, that depends.

169
00:16:51,211 --> 00:16:53,380
你们是何时发现我的
How long have you known about me?

170
00:16:54,081 --> 00:16:56,200
从你自前任站主那儿接手开始 我们就知道了
Ever since you took over from the previous owner,

171
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:57,950
而那位站主到现在依然下落不明
who we still haven't found.

172
00:16:57,950 --> 00:16:59,120
其他的前站主也是
Well, all of.

173
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,360
这可不是我干的
That wasn't me.

174
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:01,421
乔久皇帝
Emperor Georgiou,

175
00:17:01,421 --> 00:17:04,120
我完全有权逮捕你
I am authorized to arrest you

176
00:17:04,120 --> 00:17:06,120
抹除你的意识
and wipe your mind clean.

177
00:17:06,120 --> 00:17:07,260
但是话又说回来 我心里还是觉得
But then again, there's a part of me

178
00:17:07,260 --> 00:17:09,662
你更应当背负那些不堪回忆而活
that wants you to live with your memories.

179
00:17:09,762 --> 00:17:12,265
尤其种族灭绝的那些
The genocidal ones.

180
00:17:13,866 --> 00:17:16,203
你有权逮捕我
Being authorized to arrest me

181
00:17:16,203 --> 00:17:20,180
不等于你有能力逮捕我
isn't the same as being able to arrest me.

182
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:23,260
你真的希望31区 希望我
You really want Section 31-- want me--

183
00:17:23,260 --> 00:17:24,944
不止不休地追着你吗
dogging you until the end of time?

184
00:17:25,044 --> 00:17:27,380
无聊
