01:29:12,280 --> 01:29:13,682
Oh. Hey, C-Cap.
哦 嘿 舰长

1275
01:29:13,782 --> 01:29:15,183
Leave that poor man alone.
放过那个可怜的家伙吧

1276
01:29:15,283 --> 01:29:16,685
Virgil.
维吉尔

1277
01:29:16,785 --> 01:29:18,687
A round of elixirs for my friends.
给我的朋友上轮好酒

1278
01:29:18,821 --> 01:29:20,689
- Pleasure, Madame du Franc. - Mm-hmm.
-没问题 杜弗朗克女士 -嗯哼

1279
01:29:20,789 --> 01:29:23,358
Lieutenant Garrett.
加勒特上尉

1280
01:29:23,459 --> 01:29:24,693
They let you off the ship.
他们放你下船了

1281
01:29:24,827 --> 01:29:27,396
It's actually Lieutenant Commander Garrett now.
实际上 现在是加勒特上校了

1282
01:29:27,530 --> 01:29:28,964
- Oh. - Thank you very much.
-噢 -谢谢你

1283
01:29:29,064 --> 01:29:31,500
And if this unit is gonna be a permanent detail,
如果这个小队要成为常驻的

1284
01:29:31,600 --> 01:29:33,502
then you all definitely need oversight.
那你们绝对需要有人监督

1285
01:29:33,602 --> 01:29:37,372
I may slaughter you all at any moment.
我随时都可能杀掉你们所有人

1286
01:29:37,473 --> 01:29:40,242
Is that a deal-breaker?
这是个雷点吗

1287
01:29:40,342 --> 01:29:42,077
- Nah. - Whatevs.
-不算吧 -无所谓

1288
01:29:42,210 --> 01:29:43,511
It's not like you need a reason anyway.
反正你也不需要什么理由

1289
01:29:43,512 --> 01:29:45,414
It's true. You're a bad bitch.
这是真的 你就是个女王

1290
01:29:45,548 --> 01:29:47,750
- With the stare of death. - Oh, we get it.
-带着死亡凝视 -哦 我们懂

1291
01:29:47,883 --> 01:29:49,651
You're a terrifying, soulless murderer
你是个可怕的冷血杀手

1292
01:29:49,652 --> 01:29:51,520
who we can never truly trust.
我们永远也不能真心相信你

1293
01:29:51,620 --> 01:29:53,255
I love that for us.
我真为咱们感到高兴啊

1294
01:29:53,388 --> 01:29:55,658
Somebody's got to keep things lively.
总有人得活跃气氛

1295
01:29:55,758 --> 01:29:57,926
- Touché. - Yes, touché. - You make a point.
- 妙啊 -是啊 真妙啊 -你说得对

1296
01:29:59,194 --> 01:30:01,028
To us.
敬我们

1297
01:30:01,029 --> 01:30:02,565
To us.
敬我们

1298
01:30:04,166 --> 01:30:05,568
This isn't poison, is it?
这不是毒药 对吧

1299
01:30:05,668 --> 01:30:09,237
And now that you have us all here,
现在你把我们都叫过来了

1300
01:30:09,337 --> 01:30:10,238
what next?
下一步是什么

1301
01:30:10,338 --> 01:30:11,406
Well, not quite all.
也不全在

1302
01:30:11,507 --> 01:30:14,376
Ladies and gent, stage left.
女士们先生们 舞台左侧

1303
01:30:18,581 --> 01:30:19,982
You got to be kidding me.
你一定在开玩笑吧

1304
01:30:20,082 --> 01:30:21,849
Oh, I'm not Fuzz.
哦 我不是法兹

1305
01:30:21,850 --> 01:30:24,086
Section 31 bought
三十一区从黑市上

1306
01:30:24,186 --> 01:30:27,255
two of these conveyances on the black market.
买了两个这种运输工具

1307
01:30:27,389 --> 01:30:29,857
Name's Wisp. I'm his wife.
我叫薇丝 是他的妻子

1308
01:30:29,858 --> 01:30:31,594
And I'm here for when we catch up with
我来是为了抓到那个

1309
01:30:31,694 --> 01:30:33,762
that lying, double-dealing son of a bitch.
满嘴扯谎 两面三刀的婊子

1310
01:30:33,896 --> 01:30:36,397
Uh, well, we blew up his ship, ma'am.
呃 我们把他的船炸了 女士

1311
01:30:36,398 --> 01:30:38,634
- Uh, Mrs. Fuzz. - Oh, honey.
- 呃 法兹夫人 -哦 亲爱的

1312
01:30:38,767 --> 01:30:42,137
Little things sometimes survive big explosions.
小东西有时能从大爆炸中生还

1313
01:30:42,270 --> 01:30:45,107
And when we find him, I have questions.
等我们找到他 我要问他点事

1314
01:30:45,207 --> 01:30:48,110
- Now, what are we talking about? - I'm glad you asked.
- 现在 我们在聊什么 -很高兴你问了

1315
01:30:48,210 --> 01:30:50,078
I was just letting the team know.
我正要让小队知道

1316
01:30:50,178 --> 01:30:52,781
Control has a job for us.
上级给我们发了活

1317
01:31:05,894 --> 01:31:07,462
My better judgment has been
我的理智已经向我

1318
01:31:07,563 --> 01:31:09,031
screaming at me for two days now.
尖叫整整两天了

1319
01:31:09,131 --> 01:31:14,401
It keeps saying that you lot are gonna cost me my job.
它一直在说你们会让我丢掉工作

1320
01:31:14,402 --> 01:31:16,204
- We might. - She might.
-我们也许会 -她也许会

1321
01:31:16,304 --> 01:31:18,405
I told my judgment to shut up
我告诉我的理智闭嘴

1322
01:31:18,406 --> 01:31:20,475
and take a nap.
去睡一觉

1323
01:31:21,276 --> 01:31:23,111
'Cause we have work to do.
因为我们还有工作要做

1324
01:31:24,279 --> 01:31:27,683
Has anybody been to Turkana IV?
有人去过图尔卡纳四星吗

1325
01:31:29,417 --> 01:31:30,753
- Whew. - Wait.
-呼 -等等

1326
01:31:30,853 --> 01:31:32,655
Did you say Turkana or say Jur-Jurnana?
你说的是图尔卡纳还是朱尔娜娜

1327
01:31:32,788 --> 01:31:34,322
He thought "Your Mama IV."
他以为是“你妈四星”

1328
01:31:34,422 --> 01:31:36,591
Oh, Your Mama IV.
你妈四星

1329
01:31:36,592 --> 01:31:39,528
No.
不是

